    <entry>
      <title>hexo-butterfly魔改配置的一些说明补充</title>
      <link href="/2023/01/29/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/"/>
      <url>/2023/01/29/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="路径的简写"><a href="#路径的简写" class="headerlink" title="路径的简写"></a>路径的简写</h2><ol><li>为了方便起见，我们统一把博客的根目录称为[<strong>blog_root</strong>]</li><li>在一些教程里面可能会出现这样的路径说明：<span class='p red'>inject.head</span><br>其实是某个配置文件下面项的子项，对应如下：<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">inject:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">head:</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="主题文件夹路径的说明"><a href="#主题文件夹路径的说明" class="headerlink" title="主题文件夹路径的说明"></a>主题文件夹路径的说明</h2><p>魔改配置需要修改很多主题的源代码，方便修改这里给出不同方式的路径。<br>官网上给的主题下载有3种:</p><ul><li><strong>git clone：blog_root/themes/butterfly</strong></li><li><strong>github clone：blog_root/themes/butterfly</strong></li><li><strong>npm：blog_root/node_modules/hexo-theme-butterfly</strong></li></ul><p><strong>hexo-theme-butterfly</strong>是对于butterfly主题而言，其他主题相一样。<br>npm的所有插件都在<strong>blog_root/node_modules</strong>里面。</p><h2 id="自定义js和CSS引入"><a href="#自定义js和CSS引入" class="headerlink" title="自定义js和CSS引入"></a>自定义js和CSS引入</h2><p>大多数人不知道在哪创建，创建了不知道在哪引入。</p><ul><li>文件夹一般创建位置在<strong>blog_root/source</strong>，也就是和_post目录同级。</li><li>全站css/js引入的话，在主题配置文件里的<strong>inject</strong>下的<strong>head</strong>和<strong>bottom</strong>里引入。</li><li>某一页插入可以在该页面里直接引入。</li><li>一般来说，在主题配置文件（<strong>_config.butterfly.yml</strong>）里面的<strong>inject</strong>引入。css文件在<strong>head</strong>引入，js文件在<strong>bottom</strong>里引入，有的js要求在<strong>head</strong>引入，不然无法生效。</li><li>路径要添加<span class='p red'>/xxx</span> ，不能添加<span class='p red'>./xxx</span>。</li></ul><h2 id="透明度调整"><a href="#透明度调整" class="headerlink" title="透明度调整"></a>透明度调整</h2><p>在不知道名称或者找不到源代码的情况下，其实就是F12扒代码的一个过程，然后放到自定义的CSS里面再修改就可以了。可以用于类似我博客的一图流配置。</p><h2 id="一图流配置（半个对于上面说明的例程）"><a href="#一图流配置（半个对于上面说明的例程）" class="headerlink" title="一图流配置（半个对于上面说明的例程）"></a>一图流配置（半个对于上面说明的例程）</h2><ol><li><span class='p red'>blog_root\source</span>下新建文件夹<span class='p red'>css</span>，存放自定义的<span class='p red'>css</span>样式，新建<span class='p red'>custom.css</span>，写入以下代码。<figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 页脚与头图透明 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#footer</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#page-header</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 白天模式遮罩透明 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#footer</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-id">#page-header</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/* 夜间模式遮罩透明 */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-attr">[data-theme=<span class="string">&quot;dark&quot;</span>]</span> <span class="selector-id">#footer</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="selector-attr">[data-theme=<span class="string">&quot;dark&quot;</span>]</span> <span class="selector-id">#page-header</span><span class="selector-pseudo">::before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">background</span>: transparent <span class="meta">!important</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><span class='p red'>blog_root\_config.butterfly.yml</span>文件中的<span class='p red'>inject</span>配置项的<span class='p red'>head</span>子项加入以下代码，代表引入刚刚创建的<span class='p red'>custom.css</span>文件（这是相对路径的写法）。<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">inject:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">head:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&lt;link</span> <span class="string">rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;</span> <span class="string">href=&quot;/css/custom.css&quot;</span> <span class="string">media=&quot;defer&quot;</span> <span class="string">onload=&quot;this.media=&#x27;all&#x27;&quot;&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><span class='p red'>blog_root\_config.butterfly.yml</span>文件中的<span class='p red'>index_img</span>和<span class='p red'>footer_bg</span>配置项取消头图与页脚图的加载项避免冗余加载。<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># The banner image of home page</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">index_img:</span> </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Footer Background</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">footer_bg:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><span class='p red'>blog_root\_config.butterfly.yml</span>文件中的<span class='p red'>backgroud</span>配置项设置背景图 .<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">url(背景图路径)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
